citations:
    citation-agot-eddard-ii:
        source: source-agot
        properties:
            locator: "Eddard II"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "POV: Eddard. Robert Baratheon arrives at Winterfell with his court (300+ riders including Cersei, Jaime, Tyrion, Sandor Clegane, Joffrey, Tommen, Myrcella). Robert and Ned visit the crypts to pay respects to Lyanna. Robert offers Ned the position of Hand of the King and proposes a betrothal between Joffrey and Sansa."
